docs.text:
Add the plugin by adding an entry to the plugins table of your  build.settings  file:  settings   =  { 
     plugins   = 
     { 
         [ "plugin.mailgun-sender" ]   = 
         { 
             publisherId   =   "com.develephant" 
         } ,
     } , }

